name: Gardner Bender Heat-Shrink Tubing Assortment - 160-Piece
description: This 160-Piece Heat-Shrink Tubing Assortment features red, yellow, green, blue, white and clear tubes varying in size from 1/16 - 3/8 in. in diameter. Fast, safe, secure way to wrap wiring harnesses. Assorted variety has the right tubing for the job.California residents: see Proposition 65 informationFlame-retardant polyolefin resists common fluids and solvents600 V/Mil dielectric strengthEach piece measures 3 in. longIncludes 1/16 in., 3/32 in., 1/8 in., 3/16 in., 1/4 in. and 3/8 in. tubes in assorted colorsIncludes red, yellow, green, blue, white and clear colored tubingMeets UL 224 and 125, CSA C22.2 No. 198.1 and 125, MIL-DTL-23053/5, class 1 and 2, AMS 3636 and 3637, DEF STAN 59-79 and issue 3 Type 2a safety standards
